p.k: My Dog the Hero Lola has to write an essay on the theme My Hero Pet. It's not easiest task in the world for her she explains to Victor for while Pat is the loveliest animal on earth she doesn't see him as much of an adventurer. While Lola is sharing her reservations Pat ...
p.d: Despite his small size and playful attitude, Pat is the hero that flies to his friends' rescue while avoiding numerous obstacles that get in his way.
